listData.name: RAMS Action with Offset
listData.description: By linking a RAMS Action account to your eligible RAMS home loan, you could pay less interest on your home loan.

features.additionalInfo: No monthly fee or minimum balance or fixed term requirements. Other fees and charges may apply.
Defer principal and interest repayments for up to six months while you?re on parental leave with a Full Feature Home Loan.
You can make additional repayments into your loan account and then access these extra funds when you need them.

Any credit balance in your RAMS Action account is offset 100% against what you owe on your eligible RAMS home loan. No interest is paid on account. Over time, savings in this account could help reduce loan interest.
Monitor and manage securely online with myRAMS
The product includes fraud protection features
Debit card with eftpos Tap and Pay for use at any ATM or eftpos terminal across Australia

eligibility.additionalInfo: An individual who does not hold the account as a trustee of a trust or a superannuation fund, or on behalf of a deceased estate or pursuant to a power of attorney (two account holders allowed). Not available to companies or trusts.

eligibility.additionalValue: An Australian resident for taxation purposes with an Australian residential address

eligibility.additionalInfo: You need to have an eligible RAMS home loan to link to your RAMS Action with Offset account.
Must have valid email address and Australian mobile phone number

fees.additionalInfo: Payable when a payment to RAMS under your Direct Debit Request is dishonoured or when we dishonour a direct debit presented on your account

listData.name: RAMS Action
listData.description: It's an everyday transaction account, managed online via myRAMS where you can transfer funds between RAMS accounts, and much more.

features.additionalInfo: No monthly fee or minimum balance or fixed term requirements. Other fees and charges may apply.
Apart from being able to transfer funds between RAMS accounts, you can make payments via Pay Anyone or BPAY whenever you want, wherever you want (subject to systems availability).
Monitor and manage securely online with myRAMS
The product includes fraud protection features
Debit card with eftpos Tap and Pay for use at any ATM or eftpos terminal across Australia

Must have valid email address and Australian mobile phone number
